    {% if gift_card.send_on != blank %}
      Here's your 2XY gift card that will be sent to {{ recipient_name }} on {{ gift_card.send_on | date: '%B %e, %Y' }}.
    {% else %}
      Here's your 2XY gift card that was sent to {{ recipient_name }}.
